He is the best selling dance music in South Africa this year, Prince Kaybee proves that the key to success is doing what you love! The producer has been dominating local music and it doesn't look like it will be ending anytime soon. His latest album Re Mmino, not only reached Gold but within just two months after its release the album has reached platinum sales. The Fetch your life hit maker took to social media to announce that the album had not only gone platinum, but he has also reached 56 million streams worldwide. The celebration took place at Universal studios, where he was handed a framed certification. He followed that up with the announcement of a deal with Courvoisier Cognac, him and Nadia Nakai are the new brand ambassadors for the luxury brand. Prince Kaybee has also been nominated for record of the year for his hit jam Banamoya at the #SAMA25   